{"tid":227223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那製C919客機將於周五上海浦東首飛","createTime":"2017-05-03T04:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T16:37:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae09726061b0f619ab762261c71ede504accfcc","tid":227223,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T04:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170503/photo/bkncn-20170503113237298-0503_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170503%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170503113237298-0503_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=621597cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那產客機C919，連日在上海浦東機場進行地面滑行測試後，據支那商用飛機公司通報，C919客機計劃於周五首飛，如天氣條件不具備則順延。<br />\n<br />\nC919是支那首款按照最新國際適航標準研製的幹線民用飛機，於2008年開始研製，最大載客量為190座，標準航程4075公里，最大航程5555公里，其高速滑行速度超過每小時170公里。"},{"pid":"df0816341364c15cfd19402485a8604f39f56880","tid":227223,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"個樣還ok, 有d似787"},{"pid":"3e3d9aba63b016e147278e55f393db06911f301a","tid":227223,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個樣還ok, 有d似787</blockquote><br />\n抄都柒就執柒咗佢啦"},{"pid":"9ae625b767090e768e8cb47fa89b05c6a974e307","tid":227223,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"星期五將會...RIP"},{"pid":"1238f0955e1ded4db309a864f4bdd4ecebec1633","tid":227223,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd341fcc3e8e0b08250b21bf0dd031b98ab76674","tid":227223,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:23:16.000Z","msg":"讓領導先坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74942180e1712de3d72fcea7e3681368de3deccf","tid":227223,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T12:37:07.000Z"